description: This library is a .NET library that presents a simplified API for retrieving access tokens using Xero's OAuth2 API with an integrated login experience using an embedded browser. This library can be used by any Windows .NET desktop application, however is most useful for applications using WinForms or WPF (Windows Presentation Foundation). Our library enables your application to easily authenticate with Xero, reducing development effort and complexity of implementation.
